metadata.name: KAREN11_#1_Collaboration with NauGhtEd
metadata.description:
Digital fashion 3D model
Design：KAREN11
3D Modeling：NauGhtEd　　　
　　
　　
‘To Be HAPPY and  WHAT YOU ARE‘
　　　
I'm an 11 y/o NFT artist based in Japan.
　　
I love FASHION and dress up.
Because when I'm in my favorite clothes, I become so happy and feel like expressing myself.
　　
But I have sensory issues with clothes and I can't often try  what I want.

I hope everyone enjoys FASHION freely,  and express what you are and what you want.
Beyond age, gender, and any physical barriers.

This is my first digital fashion 3D model collaborated with NauGhtEd.

I believe there’s no barrier enjoying dressing up and being ourselves in the virtual world.
